metadata.name: Single Heart Dual Soul
metadata.description:
This art is to portray that a single heart consist of two souls. Two different colours portray water and fire (Blue and Red). Bald male and Haired female. Movements shows two different positions. Near and far. Everything is dual system on this earth. This single art can gives multiple meanings.

Created with procreate and gif animation.

1/1 Art

Collector will receive the procreate 1/1 art in canvas form.
